import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { ImageBackground, StyleSheet, Text, TouchableOpacity, View } from 'react-native';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import { TextInput } from 'react-native-gesture-handler';
import Checkbox from 'expo-checkbox';





export default class Login extends Component{


    constructor(props){
        super(props)
        this.state={
            email:'',
            password:''

        }
    }


    render(){
        return(
            <View style={{flexDirection:'row',
            flex:1,
                backgroundColor:'#ffffff',  
               alignItems: 'center',
                justifyContent: 'center',
                alignContent:"center" }}>


                <View style={{flex:2,
                    justifyContent:'center',
                    alignContent:"center",
                    alignSelf:'center'
                    
                    }}>
                    <ImageBackground source={require('./images/WhatsApp_Image_2023-02-28_at_5.37.06_PM-removebg-preview.png')}style={styles.imageview}
                    ></ImageBackground>
                
                 <View style={{
                    backgroundColor:'#8C001A',
                    
                    height: 46,
                    width: 400,
                    color:'#fff',
                    fontweight: 'normal',
                    borderRadius:5,
                    alignSelf:'center',
                    alignContent:'center',
                    alignItems:'center',
                    
                    
                 }}>
                    
                    
                    <Text style={{fontFamily:'YanoneKaffeesatz',fontSize:26,color:"#ffffff",alignContent:'center',alignSelf:'center',alignItems:'center',marginTop:5}} >Login</Text>
                 </View>
                 <View style={{
                    borderBottomColor:'#57FEFF',
                    borderBottomEndRadius:10,
                    borderBottomWidth:2,
                    backgroundColor:'#FFABAC',
                    height:230,
                    width:400,
                    borderRadius:2,
                    alignContent:'center',
                    alignItems:'center',
                    alignSelf:'center'
                 }}>
                    <View style={styles.inputViewA}>
                        <TextInput style={
                            styles.TextInput
                        }
                        placeholder="Username"
                        placeholderTextColor="#003f5c"
                        onChangeText={(email) => this.setState({email})}
                        
                        />


                    </View>
                    <View style={styles.inputViewB}>
                        <TextInput style={
                            styles.TextInput
                        }
                        placeholder="Password"
                        placeholderTextColor="#003f5c"
                        onChangeText={(password) => this.setState({password})}
                        
                        />

                    </View>
                    <View style={{flexDirection:'row'}}>
                        <View style={{flexDirection:'row',marginTop:10}}>
                            <Checkbox style={{alignSelf:'center',justifyContent:'space-evenly',marginRight:10,marginBottom:20}}>
                            </Checkbox>
                        </View>
                        <Text style={{alignContent:'center',alignSelf:'center',marginTop:10,marginBottom:20}}>Remember me</Text>
                        <TouchableOpacity style={{
                                          color:'#287A6A',
                                          height:40,
                                          width:100,
                                          borderLeftColor:'#59B38C',
                                          borderLeftWidth:5,
                                          alignItems:"center",
                                          justifyContent:"center",
                                          alignSelf:"center",
                                          backgroundColor: '#B6FCDE',
                                          marginLeft:95
                        }}>Login</TouchableOpacity>
                    </View>


                 </View>
                 <View>
                    <TouchableOpacity style={{
                        marginTop:10,
                        marginBottom:50,
                        alignSelf:'center',
                        color:'#287A6A'
                    }}>Forgot Password?</TouchableOpacity>
                 </View>


                </View>

                <View style={{flex:2,justifyContent:'center',alignContent:'center',alignItems:'center',alignSelf:'center'}}>
                    <ImageBackground source={require('./images/pexels-oladimeji-ajegbile-2861798.jpg')}style={styles.imageviewbackground}>

                    </ImageBackground>
                </View>
            </View>
        );

    }
}


const styles=StyleSheet.create({
    background: {
        position: 'absolute',
        left: 0,
        right: 0,
        top: 0,
        height: 350,
      },
      imageview:{
        width: 450,
        height:400,
        marginBottom:25,
        alignContent:'center',
        justifyContent:'center',
        alignItems:'center',
        alignSelf:'center'
      },
      inputViewA:{
        borderBottomWidth:2,
        borderBottomColor:'#FF595C',
        marginBottom:10,
        marginTop:30,
        alignSelf:'center',

  
        alignItems:'center',
        alignContent:'center',
        justifyContent:"space-evenly",
        backgroundColor: "#ffffff",
        borderRadius: 28,
        width: "80%",
        height: 55,
      },
      inputViewB:{
        borderBottomWidth:2,
        borderBottomColor:'#FF595C',
        marginTop:10,
        alignSelf:'center',
  
        alignItems:'center',
        alignContent:'center',
        justifyContent:"space-evenly",
        backgroundColor: "#ffffff",
        borderRadius: 28,
        width: "80%",
        height: 55,
      },
      TextInput:{
        alignContent:"center",
        justifyContent:"center",
        alignItems:"center",
        fontFamily:"monospace",
        width:"100%",
        paddingLeft:8,
        height:55
        
        
  
      },
      imageviewbackground:{
        height:1000,
        width:800,

      }

})
